## Navigation Patterns

### Plaza Navigation Flow
```
PlazaScreen
  ├─> ProfileScreen (push)
  │     └─> Back to PlazaScreen (pop)
  └─> SearchScreen (future)
```

### Pets Navigation Flow
```
PetsScreen
  ├─> AddPetScreen (modal)
  │     └─> Back to PetsScreen with new pet (pop with result)
  ├─> PetProfileScreen (push)
  │     ├─> AddReminderScreen (modal)
  │     └─> AddGrowthTrackScreen (modal)
  └─> RemindersScreen (future)
```

### AI Navigation Flow
```
AIScreen
  └─> PetTestScreen (push or modal)
        └─> Back to AIScreen with result (pop)
```

### Settings Navigation Flow
```
SettingsScreen
  ├─> NotificationsScreen (push)
  ├─> CollectionsScreen (future)
  └─> AboutDialog (dialog)
```

## Passing Data Between Screens

### Via Constructor
```dart
// Sending screen
Navigator.push(
  context,
  MaterialPageRoute(
    builder: (context) => ProfileScreen(
      userId: 'user123',
      userName: 'CatMom_Sarah',
    ),
  ),
);

// Receiving screen
class ProfileScreen extends StatelessWidget {
  final String userId;
  final String userName;

  const ProfileScreen({
    Key? key,
    required this.userId,
    required this.userName,
  }) : super(key: key);
}
```

### Via Pop Result
```dart
// Screen A: Wait for result
final result = await Navigator.push(
  context,
  MaterialPageRoute(builder: (context) => AddPetScreen()),
);

if (result != null) {
  // Handle returned data
  _addNewPet(result as Pet);
}

// Screen B: Return result
void _savePet() {
  final newPet = Pet(/* ... */);
  Navigator.pop(context, newPet);
}
```

## Deep Linking (Future)
```dart
// For future implementation with go_router
final router = GoRouter(
  routes: [
    GoRoute(
      path: '/',
      builder: (context, state) => MainScreen(),
    ),
    GoRoute(
      path: '/profile/:userId',
      builder: (context, state) {
        final userId = state.params['userId']!;
        return ProfileScreen(userId: userId);
      },
    ),
  ],
);
```

## Navigation Guards

### Prevent Back Navigation
```dart
WillPopScope(
  onWillPop: () async {
    // Show confirmation dialog
    final shouldPop = await _showExitConfirmation();
    return shouldPop ?? false;
  },
  child: Scaffold(/* ... */),
);
```

### Auto-Navigate on Condition
```dart
@override
void initState() {
  super.initState();
  _checkAndNavigate();
}

Future<void> _checkAndNavigate() async {
  final hasCompletedOnboarding = await _checkOnboarding();
  if (!hasCompletedOnboarding) {
    Navigator.pushReplacement(
      context,
      MaterialPageRoute(builder: (context) => OnboardingScreen()),
    );
  }
}
```

## Bottom Nav Bar Behavior

### Maintain State Across Tabs
```dart
// Use IndexedStack to preserve state
IndexedStack(
  index: _currentIndex,
  children: _screens,
)
```

### Reset Tab on Re-tap
```dart
void _onTabTapped(int index) {
  if (_currentIndex == index) {
    // Same tab tapped, scroll to top or reset
    _scrollControllers[index].animateTo(
      0,
      duration: Duration(milliseconds: 300),
      curve: Curves.easeOut,
    );
  } else {
    setState(() => _currentIndex = index);
  }
}
```

